50. ota_service.py version comparison needs_ota() — not in repository
health.py imports from app.services.ota_service import needs_ota. The ota_service.py file exists in the repository (server/app/services/ota_service.py), but was not included in the zip. This is a gap in the review — the version comparison logic (needs_ota(current, target)) is critical for correct OTA behavior. If it uses simple string comparison ("5.9" > "5.68" is False in lexicographic order), the OTA fleet management will silently fail to push updates to devices on versions >= 5.10.

